| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5671 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 61e4cdab-c60b-5ac7-858f-88b1f6af08cc"
